Well congrats, you've got yourself some fuel to expand the entry on.

But remember, these things are self-reproducing. A single enemy escaping, hell, even a single infected BIRD flying away and this will get out of hand. And even if you do keep it contained, what happens when you try and send personell into the base? They can't do anything at best, and at worst they start the process and get themselves infected.

Its 100% infectious, its mind-affecting, it causes death, and doesn't discriminate. Now of course, I can't say anything at all on the research project, what with [DATA EXPUNGED].

However, it may bear research into using this SCP on organic keter level SCPs.







